data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2-story, corner-lot home w/ 5 bedrooms & 3 baths, spanning a generous 3518 sq ft. As you enter, you're greeted by a spacious living area with large windows flooding the space w/ natural light, and a gas fireplace for a warm & welcoming atmosphere. Need a quiet place to work? The office is the perfect spot! The kitchen features ample cabinet space, an island, & pantry for all your storage needs. Retreat to the main bedroom en suite w/ a jetted tub & dual vanity. With two laundry rooms, household chores become a breeze. The lower level includes a large family room equipped w/ a convenient wet bar. Step outside to the covered deck & unwind amidst the tranquility of the fenced yard. Additional highlights include a 2-car garage, storage shed, a patio, and conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood; amenities include a community park, playground, & pool. Contact Tamren Sturges with The Dawn Schultz Team at 785-477-0187 or tamren.sturges@prestigerealty-team.com!
